---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Sicily | Fine Art Landscape Photography | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art landscape photography from Sicily by Fabrizio Vinciguerra, exploring Mount Etna, forests, volcanic landscapes, the sea and the quiet relationship between light and memory."
ogImage: "https://fabriziovinciguerraph.com/assets/images/social/og-image.jpg"
ogImageAlt: "Fine art landscape photography from Sicily by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
---
{% set gallery = sicily %}
{% set galleryName = "Sicily — Fine Art Landscape Photography" %}
{% set galleryDescription = "A fine art photography collection exploring Mount Etna, forests, volcanic landscapes, snow and the Aeolian Islands." %}

{% include "image-gallery-schema.njk" %}

{% set breadcrumbItems = [
  {
    name: "Home",
    url: "https://fabriziovinciguerraph.com/"
  },
  {
    name: "Work",
    url: "https://fabriziovinciguerraph.com/work/"
  },
  {
    name: "Sicily",
    url: "https://fabriziovinciguerraph.com/work/sicily/"
  }
] %}

{% include "breadcrumb-schema.njk" %}

<section class="collection-hero">
  <img
    src="/assets/images/sicily.jpg"
    alt="Volcanic landscape in Sicily photographed by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
  >

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 03</p>

    <h1>Sicily</h1>

    <p>
      A land shaped by fire, silence and memory.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="fine-art-story waterfall-story">

  <div class="travel-quote reveal">
    <p>
      Sicily is not a place.<br><br>
      It is a land<br>
      where every element<br>
      tells a different story.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% for photo in sicily %}

    {% if loop.index == 5 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Fire destroys.<br>
          Nature quietly begins again.
        </p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if loop.index == 7 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Every forest keeps a silence<br>
          different from the previous one.
        </p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

{% if loop.index == 11 %}

  <div class="travel-quote reveal">
    <p>
      Eventually,<br>
      every silence meets the sea.
    </p>
  </div>

  <figure
    class="story-image travel-image private-landscape reveal"
  >
    <img
      src="/assets/images/sicily/cyclone-henry/01-cover.jpg"
      alt="Powerful storm waves beneath the Faraglioni of Aci Trezza during Cyclone Henry"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      class="lightbox-image"
      data-full="/assets/images/sicily/cyclone-henry/01-cover.jpg"
      data-title="The Sea Rose"
      data-location="Aci Trezza, Sicily"
      data-year="2026"
      data-lightbox-group="cyclone-henry"
      role="button"
      tabindex="0"
      aria-label="Open the Cyclone Henry photographic series"
    >
  </figure>

  <div
    hidden
    aria-hidden="true"
    data-lightbox-storage
  >
    <span
      class="lightbox-image"
      data-full="/assets/images/sicily/cyclone-henry/02-stone-and-fury.jpg"
      data-alt="Sea spray rising beside the Faraglioni of Aci Trezza during Cyclone Henry"
      data-title="Stone and Fury"
      data-location="Aci Trezza, Sicily"
      data-year="2026"
      data-lightbox-group="cyclone-henry"
    ></span>

    <span
      class="lightbox-image"
      data-full="/assets/images/sicily/cyclone-henry/03-where-the-sea-breaks.jpg"
      data-alt="Storm waves surrounding the volcanic rocks of Aci Trezza during Cyclone Henry"
      data-title="Where the Sea Breaks"
      data-location="Aci Trezza, Sicily"
      data-year="2026"
      data-lightbox-group="cyclone-henry"
    ></span>

    <span
      class="lightbox-image"
      data-full="/assets/images/sicily/cyclone-henry/04-the-weight-of-water.jpg"
      data-alt="A monumental wall of sea spray during Cyclone Henry in Aci Trezza"
      data-title="The Weight of Water"
      data-location="Aci Trezza, Sicily"
      data-year="2026"
      data-lightbox-group="cyclone-henry"
    ></span>
  </div>

{% endif %}

    <figure
      class="story-image travel-image {{ photo.class }} reveal"
    >

     <img
      src="{{ photo.src }}"
      alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      class="lightbox-image"
      data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
      data-title="{{ photo.title }}"
      data-lightbox-group="sicily"
      role="button"
      tabindex="0"
      aria-label="Open {{ photo.title }}"
      >

    </figure>

  {% endfor %}

  <div class="travel-closing reveal">
    <p>
      Some places remain inside you.<br>
      Sicily has always been one of them.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>